:question: :question: ***Welcome to the first ever Eco community puzzle challenge! *** :question: :question: 

This is a multi part challenge that will require problem solving, a keen eye and a desire to explore! Thank you so much to @cooloNe and @IgreX for putting this together! 

*The first 5 users who successfully complete** every step** of the challenge will be awarded:*

1st - 500 :points:
2nd - 400 :points: 
3rd - 300 :points: 
4th - 200 :points: 
5th - 100 :points: 

Instructions can be found below, if you have any questions reach out to @cooloNe @IgreX or @Dave | Eco and good luck!!

Also make sure any submissions that need to be made posted in this channel otherwise they won't count! 😃

Solve the Sudoku by solving step by step tasks written down below. 
As you can see there are letters in colored regions, these corresponds to number/numbers that you will get once you have solved the task in each step. 
    *STEP01 is just a warm up 😆 , it will help you find what will be necessary in finding STEP02 and solving one of the other STEP's
    *STEP02 is not stated below, but, somebody will provide you instruction about it. It gives you answer for regions A&B
    *STEP03 gives you answer for region C
    *STEP04 gives you answer for region D
    *STEP05 gives you answer for region E
    *STEP06 gives you answer for region F

The order of the numbers starts where the Alphabet is positioned, then the 2nd digit should be on the upper/lower/left/right square nearest to the 1st digit or the alphabet, diagonal distance excluded. The third or the last digit, if there is, should be placed the next to the 2nd digit. 
Example: A=123, you start from A and input digits how they go.
You might need to think **well**, read thoroughly between the lines and examine all the files/documents that will be provided. Good luck!

**STEP01: **
Beep! You got a weird message from your old friend:
*
Earth, year 2082. Capitulated banks found themselves in providing human resources for orbit garbage collection. One day, I woke up in my apartment at Denver, Colorado, I looked in the window and noticed floating vehicles everywhere. Is it a dream? Surreal scenery blew my mind, I get up and went to kitchen to have some coffee. Nap might have taken a while, what's going on? On the table I notice a fresh Wall Street Journal dated 04.11.2082, I was sure I am still in 2021! Trying to understand what’s happening, I decided to get a journal and read some articles about ECO adaption on exoplanets in Alpha Centauri. Approximately 10 minutes after that, I was filled with excitement and confusion and noticed a cipher plate on the table. Being a computer geek, I tried recalling some cryptography lessons and decided to contact you. Algorithm for decoding it is, it should be something from our intern cryptography lessons, I am sure you can figure it out. No hesitations. Keys, Alice and Bob, all that stuff, attached image will help you finding decoding method and a key for it, well, you probably think of what comes first...
KQ HW QBIK NFAEOWV YMTNP LHPP. TBED MWME TTVPRVDI OSID. RBCOZ IG. GVKHM VBKG YPUE NMUQWJQ BTMF OA DLG FMURWIT BNQ NVCK I KVAILF EPY PQUW. LNYX PIOGY EPR LE VH MO @EAIO-IEC NGE MHUS NRHX UHMH. OHP I BLZYWV TWJTCM, KFY SYV UHMH04 VG - JUBCX. NIECLAAU FEUHBN MU HPW FOFE MIXO AJOB QBI CUTT NZTNWMV GC KEBD GRMU AMKFOZE.
*
Attached image to message:

**STEP03:**
You opened a door to the foyer with strong force, 
Saw this instead of your old painting of a horse.
Could it be some old geek spiritual?
Your lamp is doing some ritual…
How familiar this portrait **looks**?

**STEP04:**
You were actually anticipating for an email from your old friend, so you decided to check your mailbox. You opened your PC, log in at ProtonMail and noticed 1 unread message from an unfamiliar sender and confusing date:
SENDER: key@eco.com
SENT: 22.05.2082
SUBJECT: "RE: There are unfamiliar words in this text, and you can only understand if you are a crypto duck 🦆  or a friend of @AkaKwak🦆 
MESSAGE: "Find a **WIOF ZBUCG** in your city. Bring some **VLIGXTM** with you. (should be total of 3 **FYORVU** or more)
Make a short **SFIR CQSIPQ** together **“MY ATO UWO”** and upload it here."

Once you done it, someone will send you in DM a digits located in Grey region in our Sudoku (D).

**STEP05:**
You checked your **Windows** laptop and saw a video file recently posted on ECO discord. The sender claimed that it will lead to finding digits for one of Sudoku zone. The sender went offline immediately and left you wondering. 
Link to file: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-q5hkJXH5R6twGI_gNs8aTaplCHGYt9S/view?usp=sharing

**STEP06:**
You notice a piece of paper on the table, it seems that it came from decades ago. It is covered with dust and a bit crumpled... And there written: 

"Go outside and take a selfie with a bird and you holding ECO logo. Bird must be in free environment. Upload this picture here, after some time someone will DM you the digit for region F."

**STEP07:**
Finally, you most probably have gotten all the missing numbers and solved the Sudoku! 
Now, write down the 81 numbers starting from TOP LEFT to BOTTOM RIGHT and use it as a password to open secret note at url: https://safenote.co/r/60a6415a6f3771@41120374 to get your points!
Note that there is only 1 Sudoku solution exist and finding it will require all coloured regions to be fulfilled with **correct** digits.
To celebrate Bitcoin🍕 day, if the puzzle will be solved within this day I will add 200 :points: to a first winner, good luck and have fun!:troll:

**STEP01:**
We can find next string in message:
“attached image will help you finding decoding method and a key for it, well, you probably think of what comes first...”
a)    Finding decoding method
Saving picture to our computer, name is “tineye.png”
Name of the image tineye.png refers us to tineye.com image search website, same can be done in google photos.
It leads us to Vigenere Cipher Wikipedia page
Done! Our encoding method is **Vigenere Cipher.**

b)    Finding a key
“a key for it, well, you probably think of what comes first...”
What comes first in the sentences? Right – first letter.
Combining all first letters from message we are getting
**ECOISNOTABANK**

c)    Decoding message
We know decoding method (Vigenere cipher) and a key – **ECOISNOTABANK**
Searching online tool for decoding a string and getting

GO TO YOUR NEAREST KEBAB SHOP. GRAB YOUR FAVORITE MEAL. ENJOY IT. WRITE DOWN YOUR DISCORD NAME ON THE RECEIPT AND DRAW A SIMPLE ECO LOGO. TAKE PHOTO AND DM IT TO @DAVE-ECO FOR YOUR NEXT STEP. BTW I ALMOST FORGOT, KEY FOR STEP04 IS - QUACK. DECODING METHOD IS THE SAME LIKE WHAT YOU JUST APPLIED TO READ THIS MESSAGE.
DONE~

"Byzantine Emperor who reformed the tax code, and introduced a new form of currency. He also had one eye black and another one - blue.. Find the year he started (yellow Sudoku region) and ended (green Sudoku region) his reign.”
Searching the history of Byzantine emperors we can find

Anastasios I "Dicorus" 
11 April 491 – 9 July 518
Here we go!
Yellow zone numbers: **491**
Green zone numbers: **518**

it is **Samuel Morse**!
